{
  "name": "w04_z04_de01.ks",
  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000760\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "line": "「兄さん、お鍋の火を消してくれるかな？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "line": "「これだな、分かった」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "line": "弥恵の指示通り、俺は煮物の鍋をかけているコンロの火を\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "line": "消した。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000761\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "line": "「これでお夕飯の準備も、ひと通り終わったかな」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000762\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "line": "「手伝ってくれてありがとう、兄さん、絵麻ちゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "line": "「いや、弥恵こそ。店の商品まで作って、夕飯まで\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "line": "　ひとりで作るなんて、疲れただろう？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000649\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "line": "「手伝い、当然です」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000763\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 71,
      "line": "「はわわっ、全然大丈夫だよ、わたし、こういうこと好き\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 72,
      "line": "　だもん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 75,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 76,
      "line": "弥恵が恐縮したように、胸の前で両手を振る。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 81,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000650\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 82,
      "line": "「お店に、もどりますか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 85,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 86,
      "line": "「いや、まだ大丈夫だろう」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 92,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000764\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 93,
      "line": "「んぅ……でも……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 96,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 97,
      "line": "「家へ上がってくる時に姉さんたちが言ってただろう、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 98,
      "line": "　先に休んでていいって」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 103,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 104,
      "line": "明日は定休日でお休みではあるけど、特にいずみ姉さんは\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 105,
      "line": "妹二人を気遣ってか、半ば無理矢理先に上がらせていた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 111,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000765\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 112,
      "line": "「うん、でも……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 119,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000651\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 120,
      "line": "「テレビを見ましょう、お兄ちゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 123,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124,
      "line": "「テレビ？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 130,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000652\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 131,
      "line": "「えまたちも休むので、お姉ちゃんも休みましょう」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 137,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000766\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 138,
      "line": "「え、あ……うう……うーん……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 143,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 144,
      "line": "さすが、双子は説得の勝手を知っているらしい。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 147,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 148,
      "line": "「そうだな。それじゃあ、テレビでも見ようか」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 151,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 152,
      "line": "言って、弥恵の背中をダイニングの方へぽんと押す。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 158,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000767\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 159,
      "line": "「う……うん、兄さん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 162,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 163,
      "line": "観念したように、弥恵がこくんとうなずいた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 175,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 176,
      "line": "純粋に弥恵を誘う口実だったようで、絵麻はテレビを\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 177,
      "line": "つけただけで、リモコンを置こうとした。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 182,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000768\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 183,
      "line": "「あ……絵麻ちゃん、ちょっといい？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 190,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000653\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 191,
      "line": "「はい」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 196,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000769\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 197,
      "line": "「この時間なら、まだやってるはずかな……えっと……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 203,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 204,
      "line": "ぽちぽちとリモコンを操作して、チャンネルを切り替える。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 211,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000654\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 212,
      "line": "「あれですね、お姉ちゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 215,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 216,
      "line": "「あれって？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 223,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000770\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 224,
      "line": "「うん、えっとね……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 230,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 231,
      "line": "ぱっと画面が変わり、警察の制服を着た男性俳優が\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232,
      "line": "映しだされた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000771\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 238,
      "line": "「『春よ恋』っていうドラマの、再放送なの」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 244,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000772\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 245,
      "line": "「晩ごはんの準備と重なったときは、これをつけてるんだ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000655\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 254,
      "line": "「お姉ちゃんの、お気に入りです」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 257,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 258,
      "line": "「へえ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000656\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264,
      "line": "「この俳優さんのことではない、ですよ？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 267,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 268,
      "line": "絵麻が感情の読めない表情で首を傾げる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 274,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000773\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 275,
      "line": "「う、うん！　そうだよ、あの、恋愛ドラマで、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 276,
      "line": "　お話が面白くって」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 279,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 280,
      "line": "「あ、いや、別にそういうつもりはないんだが」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 285,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 286,
      "line": "二人の発言からすると、俺はそんなに不機嫌に見えたの\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 287,
      "line": "だろうか？\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 290,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 291,
      "line": "俳優が格好良くて、嫉妬を覚えたのは確かだが……\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 294,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 295,
      "line": "……ん？　嫉妬？\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 301,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000657\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 302,
      "line": "「どろどろ、なのです」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 305,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 306,
      "line": "「どろどろ？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 313,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000774\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 314,
      "line": "「わわわっ、た、たしかに三角関係だけど、そんなに\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 315,
      "line": "　どろどろじゃないよぅ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 318,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 319,
      "line": "どうやら、複雑な恋愛ドラマが繰り広げられているらしい。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 324,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000658\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 325,
      "line": "「回を追うごとに、ヒロインが増えています」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 330,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000775\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 331,
      "line": "「で、でも三角関係だけだよ？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 334,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 335,
      "line": "主人公をフォローするように、弥恵が言いつのる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 340,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 341,
      "line": "まあ、弥恵が夢中になっているのだから、どろどろという\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 342,
      "line": "よりはベタベタな恋愛モノなのだろう。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 350,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000776\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 351,
      "line": "「ひゃぅっ！？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 359,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000659\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 360,
      "line": "「にゃぅ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 363,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 364,
      "line": "両側で、ソファが軋んだ。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 370,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 371,
      "line": "テレビ画面には、主人公と童顔の女の子の濃厚な\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 372,
      "line": "キスシーンが映し出されていたのだ。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 375,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 376,
      "line": "「えっと……この子がヒロインなのか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 382,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000777\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 383,
      "line": "「う、ううん……初めて見た」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 389,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000660\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 390,
      "line": "「初登場で、ディープキス、です」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 393,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 394,
      "line": "三人で言葉を失ってしまう。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 400,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000778\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 401,
      "line": "「ぁぅ、あぅぅ…………」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 404,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 405,
      "line": "好きなドラマだと言った手前か、弥恵はそわそわと視線を\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 406,
      "line": "さまよわせはじめた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 411,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000661\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 412,
      "line": "「もじもじ、してます」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 418,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000779\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 419,
      "line": "「ひゃふっ！？　だ、だってっ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 425,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000662\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 426,
      "line": "「お兄ちゃんも」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 431,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000780\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 432,
      "line": "「え、えと……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 435,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 436,
      "line": "「そ、そりゃな……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 441,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 442,
      "line": "ラブシーンを兄妹で見ているこの状況は、かなり気まずい。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 448,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000781\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 449,
      "line": "「ぅ、あう……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 455,
      "line": "@Talk name=無音/絵麻\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 456,
      "line": "「………………」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 459,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 460,
      "line": "目が離せないでいる二人の姿に、そういうお年頃なのか……\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 461,
      "line": "なんて、つい父親じみた視線を送ってしまう。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 464,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 465,
      "line": "とはいえ、俺も俺で”お年頃”ではあるわけで。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 471,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000782\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 472,
      "line": "「わ、わわっ！？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 478,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000663\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 479,
      "line": "「初登場で、ベッドシーン、です」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 484,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 485,
      "line": "童顔の女優さんが、いきなり上の服を脱いで主人公を\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 486,
      "line": "押し倒していた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 489,
      "line": "@Talk name=ドラマの女の子 voice=NP070001\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 490,
      "line": "「先輩には……先輩にはあたしが必要なんですよ！　他の\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 491,
      "line": "　女の人なんかじゃなくて、あたしが！　いま、それを\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 492,
      "line": "　分からせてあげます」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 495,
      "line": "@Talk name=ドラマの女の子 voice=NP070002\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 496,
      "line": "「それにあたし、気付いたんです。待っているだけじゃ\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 497,
      "line": "　だめなんだって……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 500,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 501,
      "line": "どうやらもともと、主人公に片思いをしていた後輩という\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 502,
      "line": "設定らしい。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 507,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 508,
      "line": "いくら再放送とはいえ、夕方の地上波とは思えない\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 509,
      "line": "豪快さで、ぽんぽん服を脱いでいく……\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 516,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵＆絵麻 voice=YE000783/EM000664\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 517,
      "line": "「「………………」」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 522,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 523,
      "line": "二人は呆然としているのか、テレビを見たまま微動だに\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 524,
      "line": "しなくなってしまった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 527,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 528,
      "line": "『好き』とは言っていたものの、さすがにチャンネルを\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 529,
      "line": "変えざるを得ないんじゃないだろうか？\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 535,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000665\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 536,
      "line": "「お姉ちゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 543,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000784\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 544,
      "line": "「うんっ！？　な、ななな、なに、絵麻ちゃん？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 549,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000666\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 550,
      "line": "「……そうらしい、です」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 557,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000785\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 558,
      "line": "「ぅ、うん……みたい、だね」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 568,
      "line": "@Talk name=無音/弥恵＆絵麻\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 569,
      "line": "「「………………」」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 574,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 575,
      "line": "二人は俺越しに会話をして、神妙な顔で頷き合った。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 581,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000667\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 582,
      "line": "「お兄ちゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 585,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 586,
      "line": "「あ、ああ。リモコンとろうか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 593,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000786\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 594,
      "line": "「に、兄さん、そうじゃなくて……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 597,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 598,
      "line": "「え、あ……？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 609,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵＆絵麻 voice=YE000787/EM000668\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 610,
      "line": "「「んんぅ……！」」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 613,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 614,
      "line": "いきなり、両側から弥恵と絵麻が抱きついてきた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 617,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 618,
      "line": "華奢で、でも女の子独特の柔らかさを持った身体が\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 619,
      "line": "密着する。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 622,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 623,
      "line": "「や、弥恵、絵麻？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 629,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000669\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 630,
      "line": "「『待っているだけじゃだめ』、なのだそうです」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 636,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000788\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 637,
      "line": "「うん、うんっ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 640,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 641,
      "line": "「な、なんだ、ドラマの真似か……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 644,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 645,
      "line": "それが分かったからといって、動悸が収まるはずもない。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 648,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 649,
      "line": "弥恵の胸に、俺の腕は挟まるくらい抱き締められているし、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 650,
      "line": "絵麻は全体重をかけているように寄り添ってきている。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 660,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000670\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 661,
      "line": "「お兄ちゃん……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 667,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 668,
      "line": "絵麻が肩に頭を押しつけてくる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 676,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000789\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 677,
      "line": "「あ、あの、あのね、兄さん、えとっ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 682,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000790\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 683,
      "line": "「わ、わたしたちには、兄さんが必要、……なの」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 689,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000671\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 690,
      "line": "「はい、お兄ちゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 693,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 694,
      "line": "ドラマの台詞とは若干違うように記憶しているのだが、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 695,
      "line": "絵麻も真剣な表情で頷いている。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 701,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000672\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 702,
      "line": "「分かってもらわないといけない、です、お姉ちゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 708,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000791\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 709,
      "line": "「ぅ、ぅん……うん、絵麻ちゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 715,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 716,
      "line": "二人が同時に身じろぎをする。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 721,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 722,
      "line": "「————っ！？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 727,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 728,
      "line": "そして、こともあろうに股間の部分に手を重ねた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 734,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000792\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 735,
      "line": "「ん、んぅ……はぅぅ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 742,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000673\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 743,
      "line": "「お姉ちゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 749,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000793\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 750,
      "line": "「う、うん、大丈夫、だいじょうぶ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 753,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 754,
      "line": "また真剣な顔で頷き合っている。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 759,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 760,
      "line": "「って、弥恵絵麻！？　ななな、なにをしてっ！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 767,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000794\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 768,
      "line": "「ご、ごめんなさい、兄さん……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 773,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000674\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 774,
      "line": "「でも、伝えないと、です」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 780,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM000675\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 781,
      "line": "「待っていては、だめ、です」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 787,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000795\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 788,
      "line": "「そ、そう、そうだよね……そうなの……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 797,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 798,
      "line": "絵麻の手に、弥恵の手が重なる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 804,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 805,
      "line": "そして——\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 810,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE000796\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 811,
      "line": "「ごめんなさい、兄さんっ……え、えいっ……！」\r\n"
    }
  ]
}